@{
    ViewData["Title"] = "DisabilityBenefits";
    Layout = "~/Views/Shared/_LayoutMain.cshtml";
}
<div class="container py-4 bg-white">

    <div class="row mb-4">
        <div class="col-12 text-center pagetitlethree">
            <h1 class="display-4 fw-bold">Disabilty Benefits</h1>
        </div>
    </div>

    <section class="mb-5">
        <div class="card border-0 shadow-sm">
            <div class="card-body">
                <h2 class="card-title h4 fw-bold text-primary border-bottom pb-2">
                    <i class="bi bi-shield-fill me-2"></i>AGIF Med Benefit Scheme for Non-Pensioners
                </h2>
                <div class="card-text mt-3">
                    <p>1. AGIF provides med benefit cover to its all serving members under this scheme wef 01 May 2018. AGIF med benefit is applicable to those invalidated out of service by RMB/ IMB i.e. those individuals whose service is cut short on medical grounds and who are not in receipt of any pension. Medical benefits for 100 per cent disability is ₹ 25 lac for offr and ₹ 12.5 lac for JCOs/ OR which is reduced proportionately up to 20 per cent disability as under:</p>

                    <div class="table-responsive mt-4">
                        <table class="table table-striped table-bordered">
                            <thead class="table-primary">
                                <tr class="text-center">
                                    <th>Category</th>
                                    <th>For 100% Disability</th>
                                    <th>For 20% Disability</th>
                                </tr>
                            </thead>
                            <tbody>
                                <tr>
                                    <td>(a) Officers</td>
                                    <td class="text-center">₹ 25,00,000/-</td>
                                    <td class="text-center">₹ 5,00,000/-</td>
                                </tr>
                                <tr>
                                    <td>(b) JCOs/OR</td>
                                    <td class="text-center">₹ 12,50,000/-</td>
                                    <td class="text-center">₹ 2,50,000/-</td>
                                </tr>
                            </tbody>
                        </table>
                    </div>

                    <p class="mt-4">2. Med benefits paid by AGIF are not linked to Disability pension paid by Union of India through the Principal Controller of Defence Accounts (PCDA) (Pension) Prayagraj. The criteria for both the benefits are different and not comparable. The mere admissibility of disability pension does not entitle a person to be eligible for grant of med benefits under AGIF Medical Benefit Scheme and the principal of broad banding is not applicable to this scheme benefit.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>



    <div class="row">
        <div class="col-12">
            <div class="card border-info mb-4">
                <div class="card-header bg-info text-white">
                    <h3 class="mb-0">Docu Required for Obtaining AGIF Med Benefits</h3>
                </div>
                <div class="card-body">
                    <ul class="list-group list-group-flush">
                        <li class="list-group-item d-flex">
                            <span class="fw-bold me-2">(a)</span>
                            <div>
                                Claim for disability benefit all ranks invalided out/ discharged/ released in Low Medical Category with 20 percent and above disability.
                                <a href="~/_forms/disability_claim/Appendix_H_of_Para_62_of_AO_232002AGI.pdf" class="btn btn-outline-primary btn-sm ms-2" target="_blank">
                                    Download Form (Appendix H to Army Order 23/2002/AGI)
                                </a>
                            </div>
                        </li>

                        <li class="list-group-item d-flex">
                            <span class="fw-bold me-2">(b)</span>
                            <div>Invalidment/Released Medical Board Proceedings (AFMSF-16).</div>
                        </li>

                        <li class="list-group-item d-flex">
                            <span class="fw-bold me-2">(c)</span>
                            <div>A "Non Entitlement of Pension" cert stating that the offr/JCO/OR is entitled to the AGIF Med Benefit Scheme.</div>
                        </li>

                        <li class="list-group-item d-flex">
                            <span class="fw-bold me-2">(d)</span>
                            <div>Undertaking cert for refund of AGIF Medical Benefits on ₹ 100/- stamp paper duly Notarised and countersigned by RO/SRO of concerned Record Office.</div>
                        </li>

                        <li class="list-group-item d-flex">
                            <span class="fw-bold me-2">(e)</span>
                            <div>Discharge order issued by concerned Record office.</div>
                        </li>

                        <li class="list-group-item d-flex">
                            <span class="fw-bold me-2">(f)</span>
                            <div>Disch/Invalid Part II Order.</div>
                        </li>

                        <li class="list-group-item d-flex">
                            <span class="fw-bold me-2">(g)</span>
                            <div>Joint Bank Account Details of Beneficiaries alongwith cancelled cheque or First Page of Bank Pass Book.</div>
                        </li>

                        <li class="list-group-item d-flex">
                            <span class="fw-bold me-2">(h)</span>
                            <div>PAN Card & Aadhar card duly linked.</div>
                        </li>

                        <li class="list-group-item d-flex">
                            <span class="fw-bold me-2">(j)</span>
                            <div>Willing/Unwilling cert to continue in service under Shelter Appointment (where applicable).</div>
                        </li>

                        <li class="list-group-item d-flex">
                            <span class="fw-bold me-2">(k)</span>
                            <div>Part II Order for extension of service (where applicable).</div>
                        </li>

                        <li class="list-group-item d-flex">
                            <span class="fw-bold me-2">(l)</span>
                            <div>Low Medical Category details.</div>
                        </li>

                        <li class="list-group-item d-flex">
                            <span class="fw-bold me-2">(m)</span>
                            <div>Refusal certificate for surgery (where applicable).</div>
                        </li>

                        <li class="list-group-item d-flex">
                            <span class="fw-bold me-2">(n)</span>
                            <div>Legal documents (where applicable).</div>
                        </li>

                        <li class="list-group-item d-flex">
                            <span class="fw-bold me-2">(o)</span>
                            <div>Fitness certificate to receive disability benefits issued by medical authority (where applicable).</div>
                        </li>

                        <li class="list-group-item d-flex">
                            <span class="fw-bold me-2">(p)</span>
                            <div>Delay Report.</div>
                        </li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>